{"tid":704734,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)微光城市 世紀戰疫 刺客戰場","createTime":"2018-06-16T15:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T19:28:48.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c214f84c02cd641561e4ee969e7b27205678d8a7","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:04:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=vaVhWFyWpzlu3OhqK1rNUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=478ef73b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=vaVhWFyWpzlu3OhqK1rNUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d1b1baa2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=vaVhWFyWpzlu3OhqK1rNUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=bc8aa13f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/%E5%BE%AE%E5%85%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582.jpg&h=495bd72a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/86/Contagion_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F86%2FContagion_Poster.jpg&h=1b5508c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/luketsu/1362020957-1987790984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fluketsu%2F1362020957-1987790984.jpg&h=fbcc82c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.微光市是200年前人類為了躲避某些災難而在地下建造出了全功能的城市。建造者提供了一個200年後會自動打開的盒子，裡邊包含了回到地面所使用的工具之說明書。但因某任市長生前並無透露此盒子的存在，在其去世後消息便消失匿跡了。<br />\n200年後的很久，微光市的食物開始變得貧乏，停電也日益頻繁而且持續時間更久，因提供城市電力的水輪發電機已經老化。這個城市神話般的建設和前人所有的知識和技術已經遺失了<br />\n<br />\n2.從香港出差回國後，貝斯&middot;恩霍夫（葛妮絲&middot;派特洛飾）回到明尼阿波利斯郊區的家之前，在芝加哥稍作停留時與前戀人發生性關係。在路上，她出現了感冒症狀。她與前夫生的兒子克拉克從學校回家時，也出現症狀。兩天後，病情惡化的貝斯出現嚴重的癲癇症狀後暈厥，她在由丈夫米契（麥特&middot;戴蒙飾）連忙送往醫院後不治身亡，但她癲癇發作致死的原因仍然不明。由於該病狀會影響大腦和中樞神經系統<br />\n<br />\n3.羅伯特是一位講原則不傷無辜的殺手，他已經對殺手生涯感到厭倦。就在此時，一位心狠手辣的年輕殺手貝米高忽然出現，引起了羅伯特的注意。貝米高企圖通過殺 死羅伯特而取得第一殺手的位置。為此，他搶去了羅伯特的合約，？並且和羅伯特展開了特殊的死亡的較量。羅伯特打算在接下來一份價值200萬的合約後洗手不干， 他的任務是去殺死一個專門的竊取機密的電腦盜賊並取回一份磁碟。而貝米高也同樣接受了這一任務。雙方在酒店展開了一場競爭。羅伯特抓住了電腦 伊莉，拿到了磁碟。而貝米高則殺死了前來購買磁碟的國際刑警，並進而追踪到伊莉的寓所..<br />\n<br />\n11 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=vaVhWFyWpzlu3OhqK1rNUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a25fba37\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=vaVhWFyWpzlu3OhqK1rNUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1466c08a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9a2e07c4358d7cf2e900b4553e8217dd58783a","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd795f90fd3608011fc2fc10becd01f781133722","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae7393ccb516b66c114580c4ef418b930a5b640","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a17de3f694feb737ddf5e5490a6217672bbdde","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d224341c650a6439b5530d67dbaeb8f0ccc3510e","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7d0d401abdb9d1f020517d34d99b28c46c79ea","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4072b93fe69f1eebee06e2650d0b064dbb29b4","tid":704734,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:28:48.000Z